%N A398085 G.f.: exp(Sum_{k>=1} binomial(3*k,k)^2 * x^k/k).
%H A398085 Vaclav Kotesovec, <a href="/A398085/b398085.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..600</a>
%F A398085 a(n) ~ exp(HypergeometricPFQ[{1, 1, 4/3, 4/3, 5/3, 5/3}, {3/2, 3/2, 2, 2, 2}, 1] * 16/81) * 3^(6*n+1) / (Pi * n^2 * 2^(4*n+2)).
